beer.beer_description: Bintang Beer is a lager type of beer. The distinctive taste of Bintang comes from its quality ingredients and meticulous brewing process. Famed for its modest ester aroma, mild hoppy flavor and bitterness as well as a crisp and refreshing aftertaste, this 4.7%-alcohol beer has been serving as a local favorite for over 80 years. Bintang is brewed from selected malt, hops and water and processed with high quality standard.
